Label: AGE
Description: Number associated to an age, e.g. 27

Label: CREDIT_CARD
Description: Credit card number, e.g. 0123 0123 0123 0123

Label: PAYMENT_DATE
Description: The date the payment was made

Label: CREDIT_CARD_EXPIRATION
Description: E.g. Expires: 2/28

Label: CVV
Description: Credit Card Verification Code, e.g. CVV: 080

Label: DATE
Description: E.g. December 18 or 2011-2014

Label: DOB
Description: Date Of Birth, e.g. Date of Birth: March 7,1961

Label: EMAIL_ADDRESS
Description: Email address of the customer E.g. info@private-ai.ca

Label: EVENT
Description: E.g. Olympics

Label: FILENAME
Description: Name of a computer file, e.g., brad_tax_returns.txt, koalabear.jpg

Label: ADDRESS
Description: Home or office  address

Label: ADDRESS2
Description: Second Line of customer Address

Label: IP_ADDRESS
Description: "Internet IP address

Label: LANGUAGE
Description: "E.g. English

Label: LOCATION
Description: E.g. Eritrea, Italy

Label: MONEY
Description: E.g. 15 dollars, $94.50

Label: NAME
Description: Person name, e.g. Harry Potter, Dwayne Johnson

Label: FIRST_NAME
Description: Person first name, e.g. Harry , Dwayne

Label: LAST_NAME
Description: Person last name name, e.g. Potter, Johnson

Label: NUMERICAL_PII
Description: Numeric PII that does not fall into other categories or that the model is uncertain about

Label: ORGANIZATION
Description: E.g. BHP, McDonalds

Label: OCCUPATION
Description: E.g. professor, actors, engineer, MBA, CPA

Label: ORIGIN
Description: Origin encompasses nationalities, ethnicities, and races. E.g., Canadian, american, caucasia

Label: POSTAL_CODE
Description: Zip code or postal code of where a customer lives or works

Label: ZIP_CODE
Description: Zip code or postal code of where a customer lives or works

Label: RELIGION
Description: E.g. Hindu

Label: SSN
Description: Social Security Number, e.g. 078-05-1120

Label: URL
Description: Internet URL, e.g. www.private-ai.ca

Label: USERNAME
Description: User name or handle, e.g. privateairocks, @_PrivateAI

Label: ZODIAC_SIGN
Description: E.g. Aquarius

Label: BLOOD_TYPE
Description: Blood type, e.g., O-

Label: CONDITION
Description: A medical condition. Includes diseases, syndromes, deficits, disorders. E.g., chronic fatigue syndrome, arrhythmia, depression.

Label: DRUG
Description: Medical drug, including vitamins and minerals. E.g., Advil, Acetaminophen, Panadol

Label: INJURY
Description: Human injury, e.g., I broke my arm, I have a sprained wrist. Includes mutations, miscarriages and dislocations.

Label: MEDICAL_PROCESS
Description: Medical process, including treatments, procedures and tests. E.g., ‘heart surgery’, ‘CT scan’.

Label: AWARD
Description: E.g. Nobel Prize

Label: HEALTHCARE_NUMBER
Description: Healthcare number, e.g. 5584-486-674-YM

Label: CUSTOMER_ID
Description: Unique ID within system that can be attributed back to a customer

Label: CUSTOMER_IDENTIFICATION
Description: E.g. Social Security Number or Passport number or driver’s license number, e.g. D6101-40706-60905

Label: PASSWORD
Description: E.g. secret_password

Label: PHYSICAL_ATTRIBUTE
Description: A body attribute, e.g. I’m 190cm tall. i.e. height, weight, or any other body part measurement of a customer

Label: POLITICAL_AFFILIATION
Description: E.g. Democrat, Republican

Label: PICTURE
Description: A picture of a person  or product
